              Stop mistakes<br />
              <span style="color:#059669;">before they reach<br class="hidden lg:block" />the order window.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-[640px] mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-3 fade-up" style="color:#71717a;">
              Think Apple Watch stress monitor, but for trading discipline — detecting 7 behavioral patterns in real time, calibrated to your own style, before the slip becomes a loss.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs md:text-sm max-w-[640px] mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-6 fade-up" style="color:#a1a1aa;">
              Revenge trading · overtrading · stop manipulation · oversizing. Responds with alerts, cooldowns, entry blocks, or broker disconnect.
            </p>
            <!-- Trust signal chips -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center lg:justify-start gap-x-5 gap-y-2 mb-7 fade-up">
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium" style="color:#3f3f46;">Adaptive learning</span>
              </div>
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium" style="color:#3f3f46;">Discipline in real stats</span>
              </div>
              <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium" style="color:#3f3f46;">Journal &amp; Report</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- CTAs -->
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-center lg:justify-start gap-3 fade-up">
              <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-lg font-semibold" style="background:#059669; color:white; border:1px solid #059669;">Start 7-day free trial</a>
              <a href="#video-demo" class="btn btn-lg font-semibold" style="border:1.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2); color:#18181b; background:transparent;">Watch 90-sec demo</a>
            </div>
            <!-- Reassurance line under CTAs -->
